Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not actually a coincidence, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko told you to come, didn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the car around.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get any of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tear me away from Kouko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the car around!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't chase after her, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't chase Kouko.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, you're not telling me to let you see Kouko.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to face her,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you're waiting for her to change her mind and return.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awfully laid back of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Kouko was thinking when she left you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she suddenly asked me something not long ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.98,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When does a doctor prescribe anti-anxiety medication for a patient?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-anxiety medication...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.44,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked if it meant the patient was insecure and in pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I nodded, and the conversation ended.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.87,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, have you been prescribed any medications?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to draw any conclusions from your answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.13,0:04:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I think it may be the reason that\N Kouko reconsidered her relationship with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Kouko know...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I was taking that medication?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay out here a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do a little longer?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going... to the convenience store!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? The convenience store, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of know what's going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda told me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought red-bean soup without looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go figure.
