Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.99,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about your fall from the bridge and your amnesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.45,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\bord3\fnIgnite the Light\b0\frz344.4\fscx60\fscy60\pos(927,715.5)\c&HABBCCF&\3c&HABBCCF&}Homemade Style \NRed-Bean Soup
